                <section id="reviews" class="open">
        <hgroup><h2><a href="index.html">Reviews <span lang="th">วิจารณ์</span></a></h2></hgroup>

            
            
            
            
            
            
                                  <div class="container">

                                <section id="intro">
            <p>
              We are always interested in what you think about us. So let us know
              and write down your thoughts…
            </p>
            <p>
              Or just a nice, little poem?
            </p>
          </section>
  
<div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div id="comments-6">
        
            <article id="comment-734">
              <time datetime="2011-04-01">April 01, 2011</time>
              <p>I went on Thursday evening and it was amazing. The service was so quick and despite the fact that it was heaving the atmosphere was amazing! the food was fantastic. I went with my 14 nearly 15 year old daughter who has never tried thai food and she was a bit unsure but she loved it! Such great value for money as well!</p>
              <p class="author">From Fiona</p>
    
            </article>


            <article id="comment-730">
              <time datetime="2011-03-16">March 16, 2011</time>
              <p>Busaba Restaurant in Panton Street. Wonderful meal! The food is very well cooked, tasty and well presented. Green curry fried rice with chicken and ginger and honey tea really superb! The wooden furniture is stylish and create a warm ambience. Elegant and welcoming place with friendly, kind and helpful staff !</p>
              <p class="author">From Nathan & Francesco</p>
    
            </article>


            <article id="comment-685">
              <time datetime="2011-02-18">February 18, 2011</time>
              <p>I just wanted to let you know what a wonderful meal my wife and I had at your Westfield brach last week. It was such a pleasure to find a Thai restaurant in London with such good quality food and great staff to match. We will recommend to our friends and will definitely be back! Many thanks!</p>
              <p class="author">From Mike</p>
    
            </article>


            <article id="comment-681">
              <time datetime="2011-02-17">February 17, 2011</time>
              <p>Excellent food and a brilliant buzzy atmosphere. Best of all, is the amazing service. Peter, the manager, in particular is a real gem. Well done!</p>
              <p class="author">From Mike</p>
    
            </article>


            <article id="comment-673">
              <time datetime="2011-02-07">February 07, 2011</time>
              <p>I took my son (11) to the restaurant at Bicester Village yesterday. I was a bit dubious as i did not recognise many things on the menu. My son chose the chargrilled chicken and i went with the Pat King Tenoy - it was amazing! One of the best meals we've had out in a long while and very reasonably priced as well. Service was also very friendly. We will definately be eating there again!</p>
              <p class="author">From Gemma</p>
    
            </article>

